description:
Mona Wales has made a good living off the desperation of others. She hires muscles like Ariel X to
collect gamblers' debts with intimidation tactics. The problem is, Ariel is the worst bookie ever. She is too
sympathetic towards the players and doesn't collect money owed in a timely fashion so not to stress out
the players. Mona Wales runs a tight ship and she knows she needs to teach this bad bookie a lesson.
Mona puts Ariel through the ringer with Foot worship, face slapping, strapon fucking, belly punching,
pussy slapping and anal finger with all five fingers . This is Part 1 of a part 3 Series
title:
Mob Boss needs to show the bookie how to collect on debt
(Part 1 of 3)
